payment.alipay_guide_html:
1、Login to Alipay Open Platform<a class='text-[#5A6D9E]' href='https://open.alipay.com/module/webApp/' target='_blank'>https://open.alipay.com/module/webApp/</a>Create "Web/Mobile Application" to get APPID; 
2、Click to enter the application, configure according to the official guide of Alipay in "Development Settings" "Signature Method" to get application private key and Alipay public key; 
3、In "Development Settings" "Authorization Callback Address", fill in: <span  style="color: #FA5151;">{callback_url}</span><span class='copy-hook'></span>
4、In [API Management], access the ability of "Computer Website Payment" according to the official guide of Alipay to configure or open;

